    • unpivot

      default void unpivot(ColumnInterface fieldsColumn, ColumnInterface valuesColumn, ColumnInterface... intoColumns)
      Rebuild result - un-pivoting provided fieldsColumn into columns with corresponding values of result's valuesColumn, as String. If provided, the newly added columns will be built on and restricted to intoColumns, even if they do not get corresponding values (would be null). If not provided intoColumns, the new generated columns will be added in natural sorted order.
